    "summary": "The user, a person with Type 2 diabetes, is seeking advice on how to adjust their basal insulin dose due to low carbohydrate intake to avoid hypoglycemia. The assistant consistently advises against skipping the dose, explains the purpose of basal insulin, and directs the user to consult medical professionals or monitor blood sugar instead of confirming unsafe self-adjustments.",
